	   <tr><td colspan=2>A little more info on Lady Telora's post about mana: at level 60, with wis/int 200 or lower, 1 point of wis/int gives you 10 mana whereas at 60 with wis/int above 200, 1 point equals only 5 mana. (Obviously the wis-int/mana ratio is different at lower levels.) So while trying to hit the 255 cap is nice, I myself tend to swap plus wis/int gear for plus mana gear.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Anyhoo, I've seen this ring drop a handful of times and never twice in one evening of hunting 3-4 hours and most, if not every time (can't remember to be sure) it dropped while camping the fort off random mobs.<br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Oct 15 05:48:03 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Brakiss VonKuellar<br>High Priest of the 61st order, Vazaelle<br><br>...be who you want to seem...<br><br><br><br><br></td></tr>
